data.title: Turn This Club Around (song)
data.meta_description: "Turn This Club Around" is a song by German dance band R.I.O., featuring vocals from pop, R&B and hip-hop singers U-Jean and Tony T. The song was written by Yann Peifer, Manuel Reuter, Neal Anthony Dyer and Andres Ballinas. It was released in Germany as a digital download on 16 September 2011.
